#######
INSTALL
#######

Installing insight
==================

Install thumbnailer::

	$ git clone https://github.com/Natim/Thumbnailer.git

    $ cd Thumbnailer/src/thumbnailer.core
    $ python setup.py develop

    $ cd Thumbnailer/src/thumbnailer.engine.documents
    $ python setup.py develop

    $ git clone https://github.com/anderser/pydocsplit.git
	$ cd pydocsplit
	$ git checkout dev
	$ python setup.py develop

Install insight::

   $ git clone https://github.com/novagile/insight.git
   $ python setup.py develop

Install docsplit::

   $ sudo aptitude install rubygems graphicsmagick poppler-utils pdftk
   $ gem install docsplit

Install redis::

   $ sudo aptitude install redis-server

Install gunicorn::

   $ pip install gunicorn

Running insight
===============

Launch an insight worker::

    $ insight


Launch the REST API::

    $ gunicorn -w 4 insight.api:app
